name: paymentTermsUpdate

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to 'Supplier Creation' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Supplier Management,Supplier Creation}

testSteps.description: Then the 'Supplier Management' page and its contents should show up
When I set the Supplier to '54556'
When i click on search button
When i click on edit button of the first supplier
Then the 'Supplier Address Book Creation' form should show up
Then the 'Supplier Name' accordion form should open
When I set the 'Alpha Name' to 'TEST SUPPLIER EDITED'
When I click on accordion 'Continue' button
Then the 'Mailing List' accordion form should open
When I click on 'Add' button
When I set the 'City' to 'Makati'
When I set the 'Country' to 'Philippines'
When I click on accordion 'Continue' button
Then the 'Contact Information' accordion form should open
When I click on footer 'Continue' button
Then the 'Supplier Master Creation' form should show up
Then the 'Internal Information Part 1' accordion form should open
When I set the 'Supplier Currency' to 'PHP'
When I set the Tax Rate/Area to 'KF1'
When I type the 'Payment Terms' to '30'
Then the payment terms dropdown options should be empty
When I type the 'Payment Terms' to '030'
Then the payment terms dropdown options should display a single option
When I set the 'Payment Terms' to '030'
When I set the 'Payment Instrument' to 'Cash Payment'
When I click on accordion 'Continue' button
Then the 'Internal Information Part 1' accordion form should open
When I set the 'Adjustment Schedule' to 'SUPPLIER'
When I click on 'Save' button
Then the 'Vendor Addressbook Updated Successfully' modal should show up

title: Payment terms update
